            <div class="entry-problem"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;">㉠~㉤ 중, 이 글의 시대적 배경을 드러내는 소재를 <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:black;">모두</span> 골라 묶은 것은?</p><div class="level4"><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">① </span>㉠, ㉢</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">② </span>㉠, ㉣</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">③ </span>㉡, ㉢</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">④ </span>㉡, ㉤</p></div><div class="sel_list"><p class="para0" style="text-align:left;"><span class="sel_num_po">⑤ </span>㉣, ㉤</p></div></div></div>
